much more will the blood of Christ, who through the eternal Spirit "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 3:18","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 1:7","book":"1Jn","chapter":1,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" offered himself without blemish to God, cleanse our "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss read your"},{"kind":"text","text":" consciences from dead works so that we can serve the living God? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ti 2:14","book":"Tit","chapter":2,"verse":14,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 6:1","book":"Heb","chapter":6,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 10:2","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":2,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 10:22","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":22,"letter":"f"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Pt 3:18","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":18},{"label":"1Jn 1:7","book":"1Jn","chapter":1,"verse":7},{"label":"Ti 2:14","book":"Tit","chapter":2,"verse":14},{"label":"Heb 6:1","book":"Heb","chapter":6,"verse":1},{"label":"Heb 10:2","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":2},{"label":"Heb 10:22","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss read your"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:9:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, he is the mediator "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 2:5","book":"1Ti","chapter":2,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 8:6","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 12:24","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":24,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" of a new covenant, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"The Gk word used here can be translated covenant, will, or testament, also in vv. 16,17,18."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 31:31–34","book":"Jer","chapter":31,"verse":31,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 11:25","book":"1Co","chapter":11,"verse":25,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 3:6","book":"2Co","chapter":3,"verse":6,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 7:22","book":"Heb","chapter":7,"verse":22,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 8:8","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":8,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 13:20","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":20,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"text","text":" so that those who are called might receive the promise "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 12:7","book":"Gen","chapter":12,"verse":7,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:28","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":28,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 3:19","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":19,"letter":"l"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 4:1","book":"Heb","chapter":4,"verse":1,"letter":"m"},{"kind":"text","text":" of the eternal inheritance, because a death has taken place for redemption from the transgressions committed under the first covenant. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 3:25","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":25,"letter":"n"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 5:6","book":"Rom","chapter":5,"verse":6,"letter":"o"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Tm 2:5","book":"1Ti","chapter":2,"verse":5},{"label":"Heb 8:6","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":6},{"label":"Heb 12:24","book":"Heb","chapter":12,"verse":24},{"label":"Jr 31:31–34","book":"Jer","chapter":31,"verse":31},{"label":"1Co 11:25","book":"1Co","chapter":11,"verse":25},{"label":"2Co 3:6","book":"2Co","chapter":3,"verse":6},{"label":"Heb 7:22","book":"Heb","chapter":7,"verse":22},{"label":"Heb 8:8","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":8},{"label":"Heb 13:20","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":20},{"label":"Gn 12:7","book":"Gen","chapter":12,"verse":7},{"label":"Rm 8:28","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":28},{"label":"Gl 3:19","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":19},{"label":"Heb 4:1","book":"Heb","chapter":4,"verse":1},{"label":"Rm 3:25","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":25},{"label":"Rm 5:6","book":"Rom","chapter":5,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"The Gk word used here can be translated covenant, will, or testament, also in vv. 16,17,18."}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:9:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Where a will exists, the death of the one who made it must be established. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:9:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For a will is valid only when people die, since it is never in effect while the one who made it is living. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:9:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"That is why even the first covenant was inaugurated with blood. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:9:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For when every command had been proclaimed by Moses to all the people according to the law, he took the blood of calves and goats, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Some mss omit and goats"},{"kind":"text","text":" along with water, scarlet wool, and hyssop, and sprinkled the scroll itself and all the people, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 24:6–8","book":"Exo","chapter":24,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 14:4","book":"Lev","chapter":14,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 24:6–8","book":"Exo","chapter":24,"verse":6},{"label":"Lv 14:4","book":"Lev","chapter":14,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Some mss omit and goats"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:9:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"saying, This is the blood of the covenant that God has ordained for you."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 24:8","book":"Exo","chapter":24,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 24:8","book":"Exo","chapter":24,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 26:28","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":28,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 24:8","book":"Exo","chapter":24,"verse":8},{"label":"Ex 24:8","book":"Exo","chapter":24,"verse":8},{"label":"Mt 26:28","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":28}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:9:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"In the same way, he sprinkled the tabernacle and all the articles of worship with blood. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 29:12","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 8:15","book":"Lev","chapter":8,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 29:12","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":12},{"label":"Lv 8:15","book":"Lev","chapter":8,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:9:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"According to the law almost everything is purified with blood, and without the shedding of blood there is no forgiveness. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 17:11","book":"Lev","chapter":17,"verse":11,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 17:11","book":"Lev","chapter":17,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:9:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, it was necessary for the copies of the things in the heavens to be purified with these sacrifices, but the heavenly things themselves to be purified with better sacrifices than these. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 8:5","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Heb 8:5","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:9:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For Christ did not enter a sanctuary made with hands (only a model "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or antitype, or figure"},{"kind":"text","text":" of the true one) but into heaven itself, so that he might now appear in the presence of God for us. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:34","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":34,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 7:25","book":"Heb","chapter":7,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 8:2","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":2,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 8:34","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":34},{"label":"Heb 7:25","book":"Heb","chapter":7,"verse":25},{"label":"Heb 8:2","book":"Heb","chapter":8,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or antitype, or figure"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:9:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He did not do this to offer himself many times, as the high priest enters the sanctuary yearly with the blood of another. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 9:7","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 10:19","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Heb 9:7","book":"Heb","chapter":9,"verse":7},{"label":"Heb 10:19","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:9:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Otherwise, he would have had to suffer many times since the foundation of the world. But now he has appeared one time, at the end of the ages, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 24:3","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 28:20","book":"Mat","chapter":28,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 10:11","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" for the removal of sin by the sacrifice of himself. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 4:3","book":"Heb","chapter":4,"verse":3,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 7:27","book":"Heb","chapter":7,"verse":27,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 24:3","book":"Mat","chapter":24,"verse":3},{"label":"Mt 28:20","book":"Mat","chapter":28,"verse":20},{"label":"1Co 10:11","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":11},{"label":"Heb 4:3","book":"Heb","chapter":4,"verse":3},{"label":"Heb 7:27","book":"Heb","chapter":7,"verse":27}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:9:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And just as it is appointed for people to die once —and after this, judgment "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 3:19","book":"Gen","chapter":3,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 5:10","book":"2Co","chapter":5,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" — "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 3:19","book":"Gen","chapter":3,"verse":19},{"label":"2Co 5:10","book":"2Co","chapter":5,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Heb:9:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"so also Christ, having been offered once to bear the sins of many, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 53:12","book":"Isa","chapter":53,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 2:24","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" will appear a second time, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 8:38","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":38,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 4:16","book":"1Th","chapter":4,"verse":16,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" not to bear sin, but "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit time, apart from sin,"},{"kind":"text","text":" to bring salvation to those who are waiting for him. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 26:28","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":28,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 1:7","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":7,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ti 2:13","book":"Tit","chapter":2,"verse":13,"letter":"g"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 53:12","book":"Isa","chapter":53,"verse":12},{"label":"1Pt 2:24","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":24},{"label":"Mk 8:38","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":38},{"label":"1Th 4:16","book":"1Th","chapter":4,"verse":16},{"label":"Mt 26:28","book":"Mat","chapter":26,"verse":28},{"label":"1Co 1:7","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":7},{"label":"Ti 2:13","book":"Tit","chapter":2,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Lit time, apart from sin,"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783099559089}